#. Tag: date
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "2003-03-08"
msgstr "2003-03-08"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates <filename>Makefile.in</filename> and <filename>Makefile</filename> "
"from a <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Maakt <filename>Makefile.in</filename> en <filename>Makefile</filename> aan "
"uit een <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> <group><replaceable>relativepath/"
"Makefile</replaceable></group> <group><replaceable>relativepath</"
"replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> <group><replaceable>relatief_pad/"
"Makefile</replaceable></group> <group><replaceable>relatief_pad</"
"replaceable></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschrijving"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> creates the <filename>Makefile.in</"
"filename> and <filename>Makefile</filename> in a subdirectory containing a "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename>. This script saves time compared to re-"
"running configure completely"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_makefile</command> maakt de bestanden <filename>Makefile.in</"
"filename> en <filename>Makefile</filename> aan in een submap met een bestand "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename>. Dit script spaart tijd vergeleken met het "
"geheel opnieuw uitvoeren van configure"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you must supply the path to the desired <filename>Makefile</"
"filename> <filename>Makefile.am</filename> (though the final <filename>/"
"Makefile</filename> may be omitted)."
msgstr ""
"Merk op dat u het pad naar de gewenste <filename>Makefile</filename> "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> moet opgeven (hoewel de uiteindelijke "
"<filename>/Makefile</filename> mag worden weggelaten)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script may be run from the toplevel directory (the one containing "
"<filename>configure</filename>) or from one of it's subdirectories."
msgstr ""
"Dit script kan worden uitgevoerd vanuit de topmap (die <filename>configure</"
"filename>) bevat of vanuit een van zijn submappen."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the source directory is different from the build directory (see the "
"environment variables below), it will be assumed that the <filename>Makefile."
"am</filename> and <filename>Makefile.in</filename> belong beneath the source "
"directory and that the <filename>Makefile</filename> belongs beneath the "
"build directory."
msgstr ""
"Als de bronmap verschillende is van de bouwmap (zie de onderstaande "
"omgevingsvariabelen), dan wordt aangenomen dat de bestanden "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> en <filename>Makefile.in</filename> onder "
"de bronmap thuishoren en dat het bestand <filename>Makefile</filename> onder "
"de bouwmapthuishoort."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Dit hulpmiddel is een onderdeel van het software-ontwikkelpakket van &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "Omgeving"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the following variables (but not both) should be set if the source "
"directory is different from the build directory. If the build directory is "
"simply a subdirectory of the source directory, the simpler variable "
"<envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> should be used."
msgstr ""
"Een van de volgende variabelen (maar niet beiden) zou ingesteld moeten zijn "
"als de bronmap verschilt van de bouwmap. Als de bouwmap eenvoudig een submap "
"is van de bronmap, dan zou de eenvoudige variabele <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> "
"moeten worden gebruikt."

#. Tag: envar
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_SUBJDIR"
msgstr "OBJ_SUBJDIR"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Indicates that the build directory is in the given subdirectory of the "
"source directory. For instance, if the source directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> and the build directory is <filename class="
"\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</filename>, then <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</"
"envar> should be set to <parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Geeft aan dat de bouwmap zich in de gegeven submap van de bronmap bevindt. "
"Bijvoorbeeld, als de bronmap <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk</filename> "
"is en de bouwmap is <filename class=\"directory\">kdesdk/obj-i386-linux</"
"filename>, dan zou <envar>OBJ_SUBDIR</envar> ingesteld moeten worden op "
"<parameter>obj-i386-linux</parameter>."

#. Tag: envar
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"
msgstr "OBJ_REPLACEMENT"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <command>sed</command> expression that is used to transform the source "
"directory into the build directory. For instance, if the source directory is "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/src/kdesdk</filename> and the build "
"directory is <filename class=\"directory\">~/src/kdesdk-obj</filename>, then "
"<envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</envar> should be set to <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-"
"obj#</parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Een <command>sed</command> expressie die wordt gebruikt om de bronmap om te "
"vormen in de bouwmap. Bijvoorbeeld, als de bronmap <filename class="
"\"directory\">~/src/kdesdk</filename> is en de bouwmap is <filename class="
"\"directory\">~/src/kdesdk-obj</filename>, dan zou <envar>OBJ_REPLACEMENT</"
"envar> ingesteld moeten worden op <parameter>s#kdesdk#kdesdk-obj#</"
"parameter>."

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_makefile.1.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Zie ook"

